EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This report documents the data quality assessment for NovaMart's e-commerce
operations dataset covering January 2023 - December 2024. The dataset contains
166,381 records across 12 interconnected tables.

OVERALL ASSESSMENT: GOOD with targeted remediation required

Key Findings:
- 3 critical data quality issues requiring remediation before analysis
- 62.75% stockout rate in inventory snapshots indicates severe operational issue
- ~$1.08M in refunds and ~$200K in cancelled orders require investigation
- All primary keys are unique (no duplicates detected)
- All foreign key relationships are intact (no orphan records)


